name: Kebab

ingredients.name: Beef Stew or beef of preference in cubes

instructions:
1) Mix the meat with soy sauce, garlic and salt
2) Cut onion and green pepper in 1-inch squares
3) Arrange meat, onion, green pepper and grape tomatoes onto the skewers
4) Take it to the barbecue grill for 20 min (10 each side) or until meat is as you like
additionalInfo: These kebabs are so good! I first made them to go camping. My friends were going to barbecue but I wanted something different than just meat and burguers. So, I did the kebabs a few days before and kept them on the freezer.
